    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="section-label">Featured Work</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Production systems & open research.</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Public tools, automated pipelines, and citizen science directories built for real-world impact.</p>
      </div>

